The,Netbeast,API,is,a,builder,platform,for,automating,the,deployment,of,IoT,applications,The,API,uses,automated,dashboard,controls,to,synchronize,the,functioning,of,IoT,devices,and,appliances,The,multifunctional,attributes,of,the,API,stretch,to,OS,hosting,capabilities,for,embedded,devices,such,as,Beaglebone,and,Raspberry,Pi,It,is,also,supports,most,OS,platforms,including,Linux,and,Windows,Netbeast,API,transmits,requests,and,responses,in,JSON,format